FABIAN Phooko is facing a lengthy sentence after he was
convicted of raping a 60-year-old gogo. The Northern Cape man was sentenced to 17 years’ direct
imprisonment for rape and house breaking and theft in the Prieska Regional
Court on Friday. Police spokesman Lieutenant Col Sergio Kock sad, “On 20
September 2020, Alton Stuurman and Stephan Steenkamp helped Phooko break into
the house of a 60 year old female in Prieska.    